<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Fixed-Term Contract</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .section {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.1em;
      }
      .signature-block {
        margin-top: 50px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
      .signature {
        width: 45%;
      }
      .signature-line {
        border-top: 1px solid #333;
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 5px;
      }
      .highlight {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        padding: 2px 5px;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 50px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='header'>
      <h1>FIXED-TERM CONTRACT AGREEMENT</h1>
      <p>Between {{employerName}} and {{employeeName}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>CONTRACT REFERENCE</div>
      <p>Contract ID: {{contractId}}</p>
      <p>Date of Issue: {{issueDate}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>1. PARTIES</div>
      <p><strong>Employer:</strong>
        {{employerName}}<br />
        Address:
        {{employerAddress}}<br />
        Email:
        {{employerEmail}}</p>

      <p><strong>Contractor:</strong>
        {{employeeName}}<br />
        Address:
        {{employeeAddress}}<br />
        Email:
        {{employeeEmail}}<br />
        Phone:
        {{employeePhone}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>2. SCOPE OF WORK</div>
      <p>The Employer hereby engages the Contractor for the position/role of
        <strong>{{jobTitle}}</strong>.</p>
      <p><strong>Project Description:</strong> {{jobDescription}}</p>
      <p><strong>Contract Type:</strong> {{contractPaymentType}}</p>
      <p><strong>Work Mode:</strong> {{workMode}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>3. CONTRACT PERIOD</div>
      <p class='highlight'>This is a fixed-term contract.</p>
      <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> {{startDate}}</p>
      <p><strong>End Date:</strong> {{endDate}}</p>
      <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{contractDuration}}</p>
      <p>This contract will automatically terminate on the end date unless
        renewed in writing by both parties.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>4. COMPENSATION</div>
      <p><strong>Contract Fee:</strong> {{currency}} {{contractFee}}</p>
      <p><strong>Payment Terms:</strong> {{contractPaymentType}}</p>
      <p>Payment shall be made according to the agreed schedule upon submission
        of invoices and completion of milestones.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>5. WORKING ARRANGEMENTS</div>
      <p>The Contractor agrees to dedicate sufficient time and effort to
        complete the contracted work within the specified timeframe.</p>
      <p><strong>Expected Availability:</strong>
        As agreed between parties for project needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>6. INDEPENDENT CONTRACTOR STATUS</div>
      <p>The Contractor is engaged as an independent contractor and not as an
        employee. The Contractor is responsible for their own tax obligations
        and social security contributions.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>7. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</div>
      <p>All work product, deliverables, and intellectual property created
        during the course of this contract shall be the exclusive property of
        the Employer.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>8. CONFIDENTIALITY</div>
      <p>The Contractor agrees to maintain confidentiality of all proprietary
        information and trade secrets of the Employer both during and after the
        contract period.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>9. TERMINATION</div>
      <p>Either party may terminate this contract with written notice:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>By mutual agreement at any time</li>
        <li>For cause (breach of contract): Immediate termination</li>
        <li>Without cause: 2 weeks written notice</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='section'>
      <div class='section-title'>10. GOVERNING LAW</div>
      <p>This contract shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the
        laws of the Federal Republic of Nigeria.</p>
    </div>

    <div class='signature-block'>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          <strong>Employer Signature</strong><br />
          Name:
          {{employerName}}<br />
          {{#if employerSignedAt}}
            Date:
            {{employerSignedAt}}<br />
            IP:
            {{employerSignatureIp}}
          {{else}}
            Date: _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='signature'>
        <div class='signature-line'>
          <strong>Contractor Signature</strong><br />
          Name:
          {{employeeName}}<br />
          {{#if employeeSignedAt}}
            Date:
            {{employeeSignedAt}}<br />
            IP:
            {{employeeSignatureIp}}
          {{else}}
            Date: _________________
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='footer'>
      <p>Contract processed through JobStack Talent Solutions</p>
      <p>This is a legally binding document. Please read carefully before
        signing.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>